    <p class="micro">microcopy her</p>
</section>

<section id="section3">
    <p class="micro">microcopy her</p>
    <h3>My approach</h3>
    <div id="section3_1">
      <div>
       <p >__My approach to production is centered around emotion, energy, and atmosphere. 
       I’m less interested in perfection and more interested in capturing something that feels alive and honest. 
